  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This investment aims to increase utilisation and quality of key nutrition and health services and improve nutrition-related behavior change. Over five years (2020-2025), the programme will support the Government of Lesotho (GOL) in the provision of nutrition-related interventions and essential health services at the community level and in public facilities. It will also strengthen the effectiveness of government in its stewardship function for health and in providing an enabling environment for nutrition.</narrative>
